<div class="alert alert-info m-alert m-alert--icon m-alert--air m-alert--square m--margin-bottom-30" role="alert">
    <div class="m-alert__icon">
        <i class="flaticon-exclamation-1"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="m-alert__text">
        JQVMap is a jQuery plugin that renders Vector Maps with resizable Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG).
        For more info please check out <a class="m-link m-link--brand m--font-bold" href="http://jqvmap.com/" target="_blank">the official documentation.</a> 
    </div>            
</div>

